Class PSLSerializerExplicit

  • public class PSLSerializerExplicit
extends AgclProcessingSwitch<java.lang.String>
    An explicit serializer for PSL formulas. We need it because the NuSMV parser uses different precedence for certain operators and the standard Xtext serializer cannot be customized to emit parenthesis in the appropriate places.
    Author:
    Ernesto Posse
